NAME
    Catalyst::Plugin::Authentication::Credential::Flickr - Flickr
    authentication for Catalyst

SYNOPSIS
        use Catalyst qw/
          Authentication
          Authentication::Credential::Flickr
          Session
          Session::Store::FastMmap
          Session::State::Cookie
          /;
    
        MyApp->config(
            authentication => {
                use_session => 1,
                flickr      => {
                    key    => 'your api_key',
                    secret => 'your secret_key',
                },
            },
        );
    
        sub default : Private {
            my ( $self, $c ) = @_;
    
            if ( $c->authenticate_flickr ) {
                # $c->user setted
            }
        }
    
        # redirect flickr's login form
        sub login : Local {
            my ( $self, $c ) = @_;
            $c->res->redirect( $c->authenticate_flickr_url('read') );
        }
    
        # login callback url
        sub auth : Path('/flickr') {
            my ( $self, $c ) = @_;
            if ( $c->authenticate_flickr ) {
                $c->res->redirect( $c->uri_for('/') );
            }
        }

DESCRIPTION
    This module provide authentication via Flickr, useing it's api.

EXTENDED METHODS
  setup
METHODS
  authenticate_flickr_url
  authenticate_flickr
